Sub-projects
============

While the core of OASIS is a standalone product, several other projects take
advantages of OASIS metadata:

* [oasis2debian](oasis2debian.html): convert an OASIS enabled project into a
  Debian package
* [oasis2opam](oasis2opam.html): convert an OASIS enabled project into an OPAM
  package

